Tom Boogizm

              Devil On The Cross
            
              (Shotta Tapes)
label: Shotta Tapes
description:
All out styles-upon-styles from Tom Boogizm, running 3hrs from Greek concrète to road rap, digi dub and shite that’s yet to be named, on the latest Shotta shot. 

Meter-oblivious and mad in the head, ‘Devil on the Cross’ follows Boogizm’s rags around South African house, UK drill, and dancehall with a far more open agenda this time. Titled after his favourite book - by... more

label: The Trilogy Tapes
description:
Jon K furnishes TTT with an exemplary, feature-length double mixtape five years on from his cherished ‘Loukanikos dance’ selection for Reel Torque. Trust us, gems galore on this one.
